from sklearn.datasets import make_moons

X,y=make_moons(n_samples=2000,noise=0.05,random_state=0)

kmeans=KMeans(n_clusters=2)
kmeans.fit(X)
y_pred=kmeans.predict(X)

plt.scatter(X[:,0],X[:,1],c=y_pred,cmap=mglearn.cm2,s=60,edgecolors='k')
plt.scatter(kmeans.cluster_centers_[:,0],kmeans.cluster_centers_[:,1],
            marker='^',c=[mglearn.cm2(0),mglearn.cm2(1)],s=100,linewidth=2,
            edgecolors='k')

plt.xlabel("feature 0")
plt.ylabel("feature 1")

def featureNormalize(X):
  mu=np.mean(X,axis=0)#평균
  std=np.std(X,axis=0)#표준편차

  X_norm=(X-mu)/std
  return X_norm,mu,std

X,mu,std=featureNormalize(X)
print(X.shape)

In [58]:
X,y=make_moons(n_samples=200,noise=0.05,random_state=0)

scaler=StandardScaler()
scaler.fit(X)
X=scaler.transform(X)

clustre_algos=[KMeans(n_clusters=2),
               AgglomerativeClustering(n_clusters=2),
               DBSCAN()]
random_state=np.random.RandomState(seed=0)
random_clusters=random_state.randint(low=0,high=2,size=len(X))
In [65]:
fig,axes=plt.subplots(1,4,figsize=(15,3),
                      subplot_kw={'xticks':(),'yticks':()})

axes[0].scatter(X[:,0],X[:,1],c=random_clusters,
                cmap=mglearn.cm3,s=60,edgecolors='black')
axes[0].set_title("random assignment -ARI:{:.2f}".format(
    adjusted_rand_score(y,random_clusters)
))
for ax,algo in zip(axes[1:],clustre_algos):
  clusters=algo.fit_predict(X)
  ax.scatter(X[:,0],X[:,1],c=clusters,
             cmap=mglearn.cm3,s=60,edgecolors='black')
  ax.set_title("{} -ARI: {:.2f}".format(
      algo.__class__.__name__,
      adjusted_rand_score(y,clusters)
  ))
In [67]:
from sklearn.metrics.cluster import silhouette_score
fig,axes=plt.subplots(1,4,figsize=(15,3),
                     subplot_kw={'xticks':(),'yticks':()})
axes[0].scatter(X[:,0],X[:,1],c=random_clusters,
                cmap=mglearn.cm3,s=60,edgecolors='black')
axes[0].set_title("random assignment -ARI:{:.2f}".format(
    adjusted_rand_score(y,random_clusters)
))
for ax, algo in zip(axes[1:],clustre_algos):
  clusters=algo.fit_predict(X)
  ax.scatter(X[:,0],X[:,1],c=clusters,
             cmap=mglearn.cm3,s=60,edgecolors='black')
  ax.set_title("{}-ARI:{:.2f}".format(
      algo.__class__.__name__,
      silhouette_score(X,clusters)
  ))
